by Prof. Wasfy B Mikhael, IEEE Fellow, School of Electrical
Engineering and Computer Science, University of Central Florida,
Orlando, Florida, USA


Plenary Speaker 5
Non-Linear Symbolic Program Analysis for Increased Parallelization
