University of Texas at San Antonio, U.S.A.


Plenary Speaker 6
Information Aggregation as one of the Pillars of Intelligent Systems
by Prof. Imre J. Rudas, Institute of Intelligent Engineering Systems,
John von Neumann Faculty of Informatics, Hungary.


Plenary Speaker 7
Numerical and Parametrical Optimisation for the Simulation of a
Turbulent Combustion Phenomenon in a Well-Stirred Reactor in Steady
State Conditions by Professor Vincenzo Niola, Department of Mechanical
Engineering for Energetic, University of Naples "Federico II", ITALY.


Plenary Speaker 8
